Ing'''Bkerke''' ([[Arabic]]: بكركي malyari muring '''Bkerké''' or '''Bkerkeh''') ing sentru ning [[Maronite]] Catholic Patriarchate, a maki katas a  650 m king babo ning bay of [[Jounieh]] king [[Lebanon]].  

Anyang purmeru, atyu king [[Antioch]] ing sentru ning [[Maronite]] Catholic Patriarchate, oneng uling king pamanalipit (persecution), miyalis ya ini king Saint Maron's Monastery king Ilug [[Orontes]], at kaybat, kareng miyayaliwang lugal king [[Bunduk ning Lebanon]] (Mount Lebanon), antimo ding Kfarhay, Yanouh, Mayphouk, Lehfed, Habeel, Kfifan, Al Kafr, ampong Hardeen king labuad ning [[Byblos]]. Kaybat, miyalis ya king Qannoubine king [[Lambak ning Kadisha]] (Kadisha Valley) uli ning lalung mabayat a pamanalipit, at meluat ya karin manibat anyang 1440 anggang 1823, nung kapilan miyalis ya king [[Dimane]], at katataulian king Bkerke.<ref>http://www.mari.org/JMS/october98/The_Maronite_Patriarchate.htm</ref> Ngeni, gagamitan de reng Patriarkang Maronite ing Dimane antimong tuknangan a pangkaleldo (summer residence), at ing Bkerke antimong tuknangang pangkarimla (winter residence).<ref>http://phoenicia.org/maronites.html</ref>

